Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,MALICE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[cheeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[inaudible]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,COMING OF AGE CEREMONY\NNHN NEWS 9
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Gevanni] Near, it's all taken care of.\NI did exactly as you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Good…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[chains rattling]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[pen scratching on paper]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,MATSUMOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"T." That is all I have to tell you today.\NWe'll talk soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami] Very well. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I also have a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] Yes. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've confirmed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone hangs up]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] You got a text?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I WANT TO SEE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, it says she wants to see you!\NMan, I'm so jealous. [sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I've done it. That's the sign\Nof confirmation from Mikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, all I have to do is wait for Near\Nto request a meeting face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Game over, Near! I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew what your move would be\Nfrom the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-[monitor beeps]\N-Sir, this is Gevanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been checking the notebook regularly\Nas you ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For the past three days, he's continued\Nfilling out one page every night
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,after midnight as he usually does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The victims still match up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's been no change\Nin Mikami's behavior otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[clock ticking slowly]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[monitor beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Light] He called!\N-[Near] L?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is L. What is it, Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] I want to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] There is something I must show you\Npertaining to the Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] But... don't you suspect me\Nof being Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think it's wise\Nto reveal your face to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] That's true. I cannot show you\Nunless I reveal my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the very act\Nof showing my face will prove something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And that will bring this case to a close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[all gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as I'm concerned, the sooner you\Nrealize you're wrong about me, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] The time has finally come\Nfor Near to prove that Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But on the other hand, if that's true,\Nthis will be a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,for Light to kill Near.\NIt all comes down to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] I'd like to lay out\Nsome ground rules for the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] We're willing to go along\Nwith whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I wanna have all the investigators\Nfrom both teams be present.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, everyone who is chasing\Nafter Kira should be gathered together
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to take part in the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I understand.\NThat's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] As I mentioned before,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,there are a total of four members\Nin the SPK.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's including myself.\NAll of us will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides our team, we'll also bring along\NMr. Mogi, who's currently staying with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As for Miss Amane, she will be released\Nright before we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll not be told where we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come and meet us once you confirm\Nthat she has been safely released.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that acceptable?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Matsuda] What do we do?\N-Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Okay, Near, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a team of five investigators,\Nincluding myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Mogi's with you\Nat the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so aside from me,\Nthere'll be only three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. That's fine.\NNow, as for our meeting place…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikoku Wharf. There's a warehouse\Non the outskirts of the southeast side
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that's been abandoned for some time.\NIt's known as the Yellow Box.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already taken the liberty\Nof purchasing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If this arrangement is fine with you,\Nthen we'll use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How about that, Light Yagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,With a location like this ,\Nyou can do what you're planning to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This meeting cannot take place
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,unless I have your word that someone\Nwill bring the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, why the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] It's quite simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If your entire team leaves HQ to meet me,\Nthen there'll be no one left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to guard the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can promise you this.\NI will make no attempts to steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I won't even try to touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as Mr. Aizawa can confirm\Nthat it's the genuine notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to place my faith in you\Nand accept his word.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I do insist that someone\Nother than L hold onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My reasons for making that request\Nshould be fairly obvious to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I understand. But I'll be the one\Nwho decides who will hold onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that sound fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Yes, of course. Then all that's\Nleft to arrange is the time and date.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Right. The question is, what time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Mikami makes his judgments\Nafter midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He most likely receives a notice\Nin the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of which people to kill next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If we take his movements\Ninto consideration...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... three days from now,\Non the 28th at 1:00 p.m.?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] One o'clock, huh? That's the exact\Ntime I expected him to pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Near is obviously aware\Nof Mikami's movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine by me.\NThe time doesn't really concern us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Well, then. One o'clock.\NThree days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[both] I know exactly what your plan is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[both] And I'm going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomi, I'm sorry, but I'm a little busier\Nthan usual today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Does that mean\Nyou can't stay until morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The police are gonna have\Ntheir hands full
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for the next two to three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I've already given orders to both\NMikami and Takada about what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be the final order.\NTo kill Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,JANUARY 28 1:00 PM\NDAIKOKU WHARF WAREHOUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[camera shutter clicking]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,DEAR MS. TAKADA, I LOVE YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[engine revving]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Heads up, we're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Lidner] Quick! This way.\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[bodyguard] He's getting away! After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[Lidner] We need to get inside NHN now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-[tires screeching]\N-[Mello] Don't do it. Take a look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safer here. Not even inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] It's best if you get her away\Nfrom here right now. Miss Takada, get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. You'll be safe with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please. You have to go.\N-[Takada] Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[engine revving]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Team A and team B,\Nstay on that bike's tail
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and don't lose sight of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the rest of you,\NI need you to find that assailant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! We've confirmed\NMs. Takada's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get her into car number seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-What the hell?\N-No, he's taking her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[bodyguard 1] Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[bodyguard 2] Stop, you idiot!\NYou can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it ends up hitting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[stammering] What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[reporter] One of the attackers\Nwas heavily armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,TAKADA KIDNAPPED\NIN FRONT OF NHN?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,As of this moment,\Nboth Ms. Takada's escort team
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and the police are hot on the tail\Nof the suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Oh, man. This is really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Is it Near again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Near, you promised\Nthat we'd meet in three days’ time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of making a move\Nlike this now? It doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this isn't Near's style.\NIt's more like…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[monitor beeps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] It's Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[horns honking]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matt] So, those cars got ahead\Nof me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How many damn bodyguards\Ndoes one woman need anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matt] Hey, come on! Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when were the Japanese allowed\Nto carry around such big guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me. I'm part of this whole\Nkidnapping incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you'll have a lot\Nof questions to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-You won't shoot--\N-[guns firing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot. He probably wouldn't\Nhave told us anything anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And death is the only way to pay\Nfor crimes against Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] This man…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the person that Light warned me\Nto be extra careful of. Mello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mihael Keehl…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] Take off everything you're wearing\Nand put it all in that box.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use this blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] L, I am not the one\Nwho kidnapped Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Then it has to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mello.\N-[Near] Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be honest with you on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We had one of our members\Nescorting Takada and they confirmed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mello was the one who abducted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm apologize for letting this happen\Nwhile one of us was guarding her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Near... isn't there any way\Nfor you to contact Mello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near]\NNo, I'm afraid that would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,While I do have a method\Nof getting in touch with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no way he'd respond\Nin the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] Before I take off the rest,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,could I please have the blanket\Nso I can wrap it around me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,NHN NEWS 7\NLADY TAKADA KIDNAPPED
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Our latest report is that the escort team\Nwas forced
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to shoot one of the perpetrators
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They are also still making efforts\Nto track Ms. Takada's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ide] Were you able to get a hold of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Not yet.\NTakada's phone has been turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mello must have confiscated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone beeps]\N-Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get in touch with Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,With no way of getting a hold of her,\Nall I can do is wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello] This is the only thing\Nthat can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't do it--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[reporter] As for the suspect\Nwho was gunned down earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,we're still not able to identify him.\NThe police are tracking the remaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mello]\NMatt… I never thought you'd be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[shivering]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-Light's cell phone!\N-Could it be her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada sobbing] Light… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ms. Takada?\N-[all gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason she'd be able to call me\Nlike this without getting caught
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is if she had an opportunity\Nto get away from Mello. Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] Light, Light, please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] It's all right. Calm down.\NAnswer my questions, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing] Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] First, your location.\NDo you know where you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] No. No, I don't know where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was put into a truck that was locked\Nfrom the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But we were on the freeway\Nand I caught a glimpse of a sign
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that said we were heading to Nagano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I think we're parked\Ninside of a building somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light]\NMiss Takada, you are Kira's spokesperson.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the conversation\Nwe had when I told you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that there might be people who would try\Nto hurt you because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] Yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We talked about what you should do\Nif a situation like this ever arose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] I remember…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I did what you told me to, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] I didn't struggle,\Neven when he stripped me naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I did exactly as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I made survival my first priority,\Nand-- and I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Light, I did everything\Nthat you told me to…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come quickly. Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Ms. Takada…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember what I told you to do\Nafter that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] I have to do as many killings\Nas possible while I still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-But Light--\N-Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Takada] I can do it.\N-[phone hangs up]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Aizawa, Ide, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda, you stay here and take care\Nof headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,KYOTO LEGAL\NGOVERNMENT BUILDING
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Takada] It's me…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Send me as many names of people\Nto punish as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's my email address.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Right, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If Takada is calling me like this,\Nit must mean that she's been able
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill her kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In which case, the only certainty\Nis that she's in a situation
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,where she can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakajima, I'm going to go to the scene\Nof the crime for this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[Nakajima] Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] All right. I got the location\Nby tracing the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Head to Karuizawa by freeway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Karuizawa, huh? Damn. It'll take\Nat least 30 minutes to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Well, hurry.\NThis is Mello we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what he'll do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I don't believe this.\NAizawa and Ide are just too stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They jumped the gun and got\Nin the front seats without even thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is just too easy.\N-[clicking]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-[gasps]\N-[heart beating]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:21:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Lidner gasps] No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Kiyomi Takada, Suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,January 26, 2013, 2:32 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Burns to death by setting fire\Nto everything around her…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,including everything she wrote on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music playing]